Command#signup

Hello <%= @user.email %>,

Thank you for signing up with PostcardMailer.us! We're excited to have you on board.

Note: Your account is pending verification. We'll notify you once your account has been verified and you can start sending postcards.

GETTING STARTED

Here's how to use our service:

2. ADD AN ADDRESS
   - Send an email to $nickname@postcardmailer.us
   - Use 'adduser' as the subject line
   - Include the recipient's name and address in the body

   Example:
   To: mom@postcardmailer.us
   Subject: adduser
   Body: Jane Smith
         456 Oak Avenue
         Chicago, IL 60601

3. SEND A POSTCARD
   - Send an email to $nickname@postcardmailer.us
   - Use the subject line for the message to the recipient
   - Attach the image you want to use for the postcard

   Example:
   To: mom@postcardmailer.us
   Subject: Had a great time in San Francisco!
   Attachment: vacation-photo.jpg

4. GET HELP
   - Send an email to help@postcardmailer.us anytime for these instructions

If you have any questions or need assistance, please reply to this email.

